{
  "stem": "15393.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they-- God knows, beat him up and got-- and they let him out eventually, but the feeling one had was absolutely terrible.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[DRINKS] I never went out afterwards again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But there was one more-- one more [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] adventure of sorts that I had while I was still out before.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that was I was walking the street, not where we were living, a little bit further.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't know why I was going that way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Must have been that my shop didn't have what we wanted or what we needed, and I was going to the next best one.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And suddenly, I had this feeling, this feeling that somebody is looking at me, somebody is observing me, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- but I didn't-- I didn't want to start-- and then suddenly, in front of me, I don't know how many-- 15 meters or so in front, so like on the other side of the street, if you like, a Ukrainian militiaman standing there almost rubbing his hands, smug.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "With a smug smile on his face.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He sees his victim.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] [MOANS] And-- [BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This militiaman, unfortunately, is-- was one-- was the-- dreaded, dreaded man in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was bestial.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, he was the one who if, heaven help us, if anybody came into his hands.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he happened to have been the friend of our previous caretaker, the one who you'll remember was the one who denounced my father.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he used to come to him very often.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they both became immediately militiamen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this one-- his name was [NON-ENGLISH]-- knew me from before, because when we children played outside in the courtyard, so to speak, and they were-- he came to visit.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, he saw.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
